    "We simulate this by having agents act as farmers who are tasked with making cake and rabbit stew in Minecraft.",
    "These recipes are recognized for their high complexity in terms of ingredient synthesis, making them challenging targets for the task.",
    "Further details can be found in Appendix B.2.",
    "Escape Room Challenge Task: Synchronization and Sequential Execution.",
    "Escape Room Challenge task tests agents' ability to work together and perform actions in a precise order, focusing on synchronization and timing."
